a personal vendetta, yeah.

08:04.360 --> 08:06.316
I don't think you know
what the hell
you're talking about.

08:06.403 --> 08:07.984
MOHINDER:
They killed Daphne, Matt.
Daphne.

08:08.072 --> 08:10.313
This isn't about Daphne.
This is about me
helping everybody.

08:10.407 --> 08:11.863
Well, you're not
helping him.

08:11.950 --> 08:14.157
He has done
much worse to me.

08:14.244 --> 08:16.496
You're better than him,
Matt. That's my point.

08:16.580 --> 08:18.992
No, the point is
he's in pain.
Does he have to be?

08:19.083 --> 08:21.825
Look, the drugs are...
It's not gonna be
comfortable.

08:21.960 --> 08:25.123
MATT: l'm digging
through his brain...
MOHINDER: To find a memory.

08:25.214 --> 08:27.250
Can we really trust this?

08:27.341 --> 08:31.004
I mean, who knows what
information's been tainted
by time and perception?

08:31.095 --> 08:33.632
We know nothing.
He knows everything
that we need to know.

08:33.722 --> 08:35.098
He's right.

08:37.434 --> 08:39.686
Do I have your permission
to go back in now?

08:48.779 --> 08:50.940
Let's find out how
this whole thing began.

08:51.073 --> 08:52.028
(EXHALING)

08:52.116 --> 08:53.105
(PANTING)

08:57.579 --> 08:58.568
