09:33.782 --> 09:35.158
Oh, right.

09:35.242 --> 09:37.107
You didn't make
any other plans,
did you?

09:37.202 --> 09:38.817
No, no.
It sounds great.

09:48.172 --> 09:49.787
It's nice to
have you around.

10:01.268 --> 10:02.929
