to see me here.
I wanted to talk to you alone.

10:31.715 --> 10:33.671
Do you have a minute?

10:34.718 --> 10:37.050
Yeah. Yeah, sure.
Come on in.

10:47.105 --> 10:50.597
What's going on?
I've set some
things in motion.

10:51.693 --> 10:53.069
Things?

10:53.695 --> 10:57.187
Everything's gonna change,
and ljust want you to know
Claire's going to be safe.

10:57.282 --> 10:58.783
What do you mean "safe"?

10:59.827 --> 11:01.283
What have you done?

11:03.205 --> 11:08.370
Noah, I got into politics
so I could help people,
make the big impact.

11:08.460 --> 11:09.495
What have you done?

11:09.586 --> 11:13.044
I'm certain that you involved
yourself with the Company
for the same reason.

11:13.131 --> 11:18.467
You sensed there was a need.
Well, that need still exists.

11:19.096 --> 11:21.963
People with abilities
are a threat.
Primatech is closed.

11:22.057 --> 11:26.266
Primatech?
With all due respect,

11:26.353 --> 11:28.890
Primatech never did the job
that was required of them.

11:28.981 --> 11:30.562
Then you have
the solution.

11:30.649 --> 11:33.356
The United States government
has the resources
and the authority

11:33.443 --> 11:35.604
to contain this problem.

11:35.696 --> 11:36.936
Wait a minute.
What are you
talking about here?

11:37.030 --> 11:39.362
Rounding people up?
For starters, yeah.

11:40.450 --> 11:42.941
Incarceration is
the only way to make
sure everybody is safe.

11:43.036 --> 11:46.119
Everybody.
Yourself included.

11:46.206 --> 11:48.538
Certain exceptions
are going to be made.

11:49.585 --> 11:54.124
ls Claire an exception?
She could be,
but I need your help.

11:56.466 --> 11:58.798
What do you plan to do
once you have everybody?

11:58.886 --> 12:02.549
We find an answer.
We get the best
team of scientists

12:02.639 --> 12:05.221
and we find a way
to eliminate these
abilities forever.

12:05.309 --> 12:07.550
And if that's not possible?
I refuse to accept that.

12:07.644 --> 12:09.680
My abilities
were given to me.
They can be taken away.

12:09.771 --> 12:13.684
