to know this.

12:18.155 --> 12:22.023
But she will. They all will,
and they will blame you.

12:22.117 --> 12:24.233
They won't understand.

12:24.328 --> 12:28.947
l have gone so far
off the rails with this,
so far around the bend.

12:31.251 --> 12:32.991
I nearly killed
my own brother.

12:34.504 --> 12:36.836
And ljust want a chance
to make things right.

12:41.386 --> 12:42.887
What do you want from me?

12:44.473 --> 12:49.012
You spent 20 years
tracking these people.
I want to know how you did it.

13:11.041 --> 13:14.249
What is all this stuff?
This is the last
20 years of my life.

13:26.723 --> 13:31.638
And you kept it.
It's hard to throw
this stuff away.

13:31.728 --> 13:34.344
Noah,
I am the US Government.

13:34.439 --> 13:38.682
