a secret that we've kept
for over 30 years.

13:49.788 --> 13:51.824
I can't un-ring that bell.
I know you can't.

13:51.915 --> 13:53.451
Okay.

13:53.542 --> 13:58.332
Look, ljoined the Company
for a reason, and that
reason doesn't disappear

13:58.422 --> 14:01.209
just because your mother
decides to turn off
the lights.

14:01.299 --> 14:05.087
