angles as we can, okay?

20:30.105 --> 20:32.096
Glad to see you got
your old job baCk.

20:36.403 --> 20:39.315
How else would
I randomly bump into
old acquaintances?

20:41.074 --> 20:45.192
Something big is happening.
I need your help.

20:45.328 --> 20:48.912
Why would I believe
anything you say?
Because it's true.

20:48.998 --> 20:52.991
I realize we haven't
always played nice
with eaCh other,

20:53.086 --> 20:55.077
but you have
a unique perspective.

20:58.967 --> 21:03.006
What exactly is happening?
A government program.

21:04.013 --> 21:08.347
And it is going
to blow up in their face.
I need you Mohinder.

21:08.435 --> 21:10.175
I need your brain,
I need your strength.

21:10.270 --> 21:15.185
Together,
we can help people,
we can save lives.

21:16.359 --> 21:18.020
What do you say?

21:20.780 --> 21:22.566
