28:29.208 --> 28:30.914
(TIRES SQUEALING)

28:39.802 --> 28:42.214
Secure all the exits.

28:42.305 --> 28:44.921
Wait for my order
before moving in.

28:45.600 --> 28:47.431
I want eyes on the scene.

28:51.480 --> 28:53.607
You really should
lock your windows.

28:56.819 --> 28:59.231
AGENT: Sir,
we have a situation.

28:59.322 --> 29:02.610
Tell me you found Bennet.
No, sir, not Bennet.

29:07.330 --> 29:10.663
Did you mobilize a unit?
I was waiting for
your order, Senator.

29:25.056 --> 29:29.595
So you're the one
