Making us run, hide.

29:29.685 --> 29:31.221
Peter, right?

29:33.814 --> 29:35.395
You're the good brother,

29:38.152 --> 29:39.653
the passionate one.

29:43.199 --> 29:44.530
You want me dead?

29:45.117 --> 29:46.106
Huh?

29:47.912 --> 29:49.072
Do it.

29:49.163 --> 29:51.324
You want to die?
No.

29:52.124 --> 29:54.536
But you came here
with a mission,
right? So?

29:55.878 --> 29:57.334
Get it over with.

29:58.589 --> 29:59.829
(SCOFFS)

29:59.924 --> 30:01.585
You think you're innocent,

30:02.718 --> 30:03.878
that you're the good guy?

30:03.970 --> 30:08.054
You broke into my house,
put a gun to my head!

30:08.140 --> 30:11.473
You're the one
who is hunting us.

30:11.560 --> 30:15.223
For good reasons.
And it's not ever
gonna stop.

30:16.857 --> 30:20.475
'Cause if you kill me,
I'll get exactly
what I want.

30:20.569 --> 30:23.902
And what is that?
They'll see what
I've been telling them.

30:25.116 --> 30:27.732
They'll know
just how dangerous
you people are.

30:27.827 --> 30:29.283
He's right, you know.

30:31.872 --> 30:34.739
Hello, Nathan.
Don't do it, Pete.

30:35.793 --> 30:37.909
How the hell did you
get here so fast?

30:43.050 --> 30:46.838
I know you might think
I'm the bad guy here,
Pete, and maybe I am.

30:46.929 --> 30:48.669
But you've got
to believe me
when I tell you...

30:48.764 --> 30:51.426
I don't.
I'm done believing in you.

30:52.476 --> 30:53.511
This isn't you.

30:53.602 --> 30:54.591
(GUN FIRES)

30:55.730 --> 30:57.220
