30:58.065 --> 30:59.976
If you kill him,

31:00.067 --> 31:03.150
the order will come down
to kill you all, and I won't
be able to contain...

31:03.237 --> 31:06.946
Just shut up! Shut up!
Let me figure a way
out of this.

31:07.033 --> 31:11.777
(PANTING) That's right.
You can't trust either
of us. Not really.

31:11.871 --> 31:13.827
They're moving in
on Matt and Mohinder
right now.

31:13.914 --> 31:16.747
You pull the trigger,
you're signing
their death warrant.

31:32.475 --> 31:34.887
Why did you tell him
about Parkman and Suresh?

31:34.977 --> 31:37.810
| just saved your life!
