(GRUNTING)

37:15.234 --> 37:18.397
You believe science
has all the answers,
right?

37:18.487 --> 37:20.227
Why don't you
start with her?

37:22.241 --> 37:24.072
MOHINDER: Daphne.

37:24.159 --> 37:26.275
She is alive.
For now.

37:27.496 --> 37:28.827
But I'm losing
that battle.

37:28.914 --> 37:30.700
And unless you help me,
I can assure you,

37:30.791 --> 37:32.656
