out of the house,

38:03.532 --> 38:06.695
my daughter's scared to
death of me, what am I
gonna do with time off?

38:08.454 --> 38:10.661
You were right before

38:12.332 --> 38:15.199
when you said I was weak
because of my split focus.

38:16.378 --> 38:21.418
That's not gonna be
a problem any more.
The job is all that's left.

38:22.551 --> 38:25.042
You have
my complete dedication.

38:26.930 --> 38:28.886
You still think
I'm compromised?

38:29.725 --> 38:31.636
They found
your storage unit.

38:31.727 --> 38:33.968
Which,
