led you right to them.

38:34.062 --> 38:36.053
You're the one that
let them get away.

38:37.191 --> 38:39.227
Yeah, I admit.

38:39.318 --> 38:41.309
l underestimated them.

38:42.362 --> 38:44.648
They got away
because Senator Petrelli

38:44.740 --> 38:47.607
let his personal interests
Cloud his judgment.

38:50.245 --> 38:52.907
Kid gloves are
standard issue
in this outfit.

38:54.041 --> 38:55.030
(SIGHING)

38:55.125 --> 38:57.582
You and l have
to Change that.

39:01.256 --> 39:02.587
You agree?

39:04.259 --> 39:05.760
Absolutely.

39:47.469 --> 39:48.584
So?

39:50.180 --> 39:53.672
All things considered,
went pretty well.

39:53.767 --> 39:55.598
And I think
he trusts me.

39:55.686 --> 39:58.769
Don't be foolish, Noah.
That man trusts no one.

39:58.855 --> 40:01.141
He will continue
to test you.

40:02.109 --> 40:03.895
I'm prepared
to be tested.

40:04.903 --> 40:09.237
Because he's got it
all wrong, and so does
Nathan, for that matter.

40:10.158 --> 40:11.409
(SIGHING)

40:11.493 --> 40:15.361
There's no halfway any more.
You're gonna have to play
the role,

40:15.455 --> 40:18.367
make tough Choices,
to prove your loyalty
to them,

40:18.458 --> 40:20.039
to their cause.

40:21.336 --> 40:22.587
